Package io.github.mizinchik

Interface Tree<T extends Tree<T,​E>,​E>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - A class implementing Tree
    E - A general class in the nodes of the Tree
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TreeImpl
    public interface Tree<T extends Tree<T,​E>,​E>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Interface of an n-ary Tree data structure. Provides methods for adding and deleting nodes, for splitting trees and iterating the whole tree.
